description: Delta Shell is an integrated modeling environment. This package contains Delta Shell binaries plus a number of plugins which can be used for data processing, visualization and storage of model data (SQLite-based project file format, NetCDF, GIS, charts / tables and support for scientific data structures such as time series, multi-dimensional arrays and geospatial coverages).
releaseNotes: Preview release of Delta Shell: command-line, gui + default plugins.
summary: Integrated modeling environment with a focus on setup, configuration and use of integrated environmental models.
title: Delta Shell SDK
